description: Last season The Amazon (2-4) was ranked 7th, she faces off with last season's 6th ranked wrestler Vendetta (1-2). The Amazon is taller, bigger, and more experienced. Vendetta is a predator--fast, tenacious, and a quick study. The Amazon was helpless from the start, and in RD4 became Vendetta's personal pussy-licker. Vendetta is a monster here at US.
title: The Amazon vs. Vendetta
